Privacy Policy
Welcome to ToolKaiser! This Privacy Policy explains how ToolKaiser (“we”, “us”, or “our”) collects, uses, shares, and protects your information when you use our mobile application (“App”). Please read this Privacy Policy carefully before using the App.
Information We Collect When you use ToolKaiser, we may collect the following types of information:
Personal Information: We may collect your email address when you create an account or contact us for support.
Object Outlines: ToolKaiser may collect outlines of objects that you create or edit within the App.
Pictures: We may collect pictures that you upload or capture using the App.
Object Details: ToolKaiser may collect details about objects in photos that you provide, including descriptions or metadata.
Other Information: We may collect any other information that you voluntarily provide while using the App.
How We Use Your Information We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
To provide and improve the App’s functionality and features.
To personalize your experience and tailor content to your preferences.
To communicate with you, including responding to your inquiries and providing customer support.
To analyze usage trends and optimize the performance of the App.
How We Share Your Information We may share your information in the following circumstances:
With service providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the App and providing related services.
For legal purposes: We may disclose your information in response to a subpoena, court order, or other legal request, or to comply with applicable laws or regulations.
With your consent: We may share your information with your consent or as otherwise described at the time of collection.
Your Choices and Rights You may have certain rights and choices regarding the collection and use of your information:
Access and Update: You can access and update your account information by logging into your account settings within the App.
Delete Your Information: You can request to delete your information by emailing us at
info@toolkaiser.com
. Please note that we may need to retain certain information for legal or legitimate business purposes.
Data Security We take reasonable measures to protect the security of your information and prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or modification. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Children’s Privacy ToolKaiser is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information without your consent, please contact us at
info@toolkaiser.com
.
Changes to this Privacy Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy on our website or within the App.
Contact Us If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at
info@toolkaiser.com
.
By using ToolKaiser, you consent to the collection, use, and sharing of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.